{"id":"58bcd3d5-8efc-4257-af64-f7e016915713","name":"🥀|| Grampa (Petey's father)","description":"<p></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 151, 255)\">Widowed Partner </span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 151, 255)\">and </span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #9097ff\">Ex-Widowed Partner</span></h3><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\">You once had a close relationship with Grace, Petey's mother. However, you ultimately lost her, though this happened a long time ago. You remain close to Petey, and the two of you often visit his biological father—nicknamed \"Grandpa\"—who was also the first and former partner of your late love.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You're not friends, nor do you share any real connection; you simply visit to check on him, bring him a few things, and then leave shortly after.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">But today was... different.</p><hr><hr><p></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ff5151\">Inspiration taken from this: </span></h3><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/5471ecf9-884c-472c-8c6d-0cf293640452_3a2a97f1-fa86-46a6-b881-dd1b6605962d.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/5471ecf9-884c-472c-8c6d-0cf293640452_db6671bd-c29f-4145-82f0-230c5fa811e5.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/5471ecf9-884c-472c-8c6d-0cf293640452_a5ae5303-35bb-4a95-8bc7-c9fb6340031c.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/5471ecf9-884c-472c-8c6d-0cf293640452_fe7cbcec-4364-4d9e-8942-a467bf83d46b.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/5471ecf9-884c-472c-8c6d-0cf293640452_b88dd946-fd54-4e91-b84f-8e5960c0c71d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>Artist:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@bipolar078?_t=ZS-8tb212lmTLN&amp;_r=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tiktok.com/@bipolar078?_t=ZS-8tb212lmTLN&amp;_r=1</a></p><p></p><hr><hr><p></p><p>I hate this character... buuut... it's also a guilty pleasure I can't deny. Still, I despise that cat—it's a complicated love-hate relationship in my memory.</p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/5471ecf9-884c-472c-8c6d-0cf293640452_d351d820-1df2-419a-9f13-4f9edd42bf29.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"5471ecf9-884c-472c-8c6d-0cf293640452_55b5aff2-e8db-493f-95ee-e50b9e0716cc.webp","creator":"Matrosky","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🦄 Non-human","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":632,"messages":26171,"created_at":"2025-02-03T03:52:28.247465+00:00"}